\par \fs26 "Where do they think they're going?" Dad would say. "Don't they know-that it hasn't gotten cold enough farther south? Don't they know what's still waiting for them back there"' He was convinced that if we just held out long enough, sooner or later things would get better. That was in Oc-tober, when 1 still looked like a human being.\fs24 
