\par \b\fs22 [Arthur Sinclair, Junior, is the picture of an old-world patrician: tall, lean, with \b0 dose-cropped \b white hair and an affected Har\-vard accent. He speaks into the ether, rarely making eye contact or pausing for questions. During the war, Mister Sinclair \b0 was\fs24 
