\par \i\fs26 But you could kill them more easily.\i0\fs24 
\par \fs26 Yes and no. You didn't have to hit them in head; you could take out the lungs, the heart, hit them anywhere, and eventually they'd bleed to death. But if you didn't stop them with one shot, they'd just keep coming until they died.\fs24 
